Comment: 0,0:00:00.12,0:00:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入高二已经两个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉了新班级  也习惯了身为前辈的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待着我们的  便是这一学年…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是整个高中岁月最重要的活动之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  樟叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对我来说  这也是个特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘  当心被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没有惊动到黑暗的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还是要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出太大的声响会扰得四邻不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你戴这个东西干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚结束唤醒暗炎龙的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上这个能强化邪王真眼的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以获得洞察隔绝世界的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快收拾  收拾完了去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是要前往黑暗世界  准备如此周密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是精简过了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得还背着个包包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随身行李随身带嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：手に持つだけに手荷物。冷笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没玩够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好笑吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人奔赴战场期间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让凸守成为结社的守护神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天打扮得挺精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修学旅行嘛  充满了未知的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我来宣布每个小组的娱乐节目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了去卫生间以外  不准去其他车厢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也是  禁止通话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是音速级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  其实还没那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但邪王真眼已经洞察了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年回她老家的时候已经很不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩还是那么亲密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦  反正你们也在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心不会给别人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候打印出来给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来一小时是自由活动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两点在这里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里看起来好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗守护圣人幽禁的龙之灵魂  就沉睡在这座宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此处即是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Dark  Draconian's  Saint  Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑龙人圣殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下我要躲开黑暗的耳目潜入此处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时都要警惕黑暗耳目的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还专门把这个带过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战准备必须周全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这玩意你很喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小鸟游同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗装备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不如在这里给你跟富樫君来个合影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害羞嘛  这可是修学旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快靠近点  跟男朋友留下点美好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  富樫你在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们组的计划表在你这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去精神活动会停止的  真的要Death了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  难道说那是主人的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草荫布满捕蝇草…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：ハエトリソウが生えとる。冷笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午睡对决一役以来  你似乎更加热衷于午睡事业了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小凸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于从幻梦世界中回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里现在已经是停滞领域了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须快快逃离  向别处进击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往哪里进击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印着黑暗力量的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说从绳文时代起这里就有人居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且附近曾经是一片海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气四处弥漫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟游同学  你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和从太古时代起存在于此处的灵魂对话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明使者的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑·弥·呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  我什么都没说  什么都没说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟游同学在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害羞啦  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再开你们玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  小鸟游同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小鸟游同学你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩真是太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经在交往了  没必要这么怕羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我和勇太只是契约关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是恋人契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王曲地腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这种地方胡闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生谷  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个房间的人要按规定时间去洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  你们一想到在恋爱就变得不自然了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可是恋人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙其实是不知道该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中二病设定和恋爱之间似乎无法完美协调
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能把她暂时拜托给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样好吗  你们不想单独在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样  但是大家都会注意到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花她不太适应这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你也挺温柔的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是温柔吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没事我来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  反正我们都闲成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}无聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲷鱼袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs36}注：鯛、靴下。冷笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些  我关心的是漆黑烈焰使和主人之间的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凸很激动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守一直都在意着他们是不是想要独处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他们到底想还是不想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在家里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人老是偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像是我在碍事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你  我非常能理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dark·Flame  Master  &  GelZone  UNSAS'  Little  Sister！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我樟叶就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟叶你一定很喜欢哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大家现在在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们真的要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  还是别这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你已经有小鸟游同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色他被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的只是搞错了男浴室和女浴室而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一色…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样  只能采取B路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点我们班的女生就要洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…丹生谷同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗  丹生挺受欢迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  没有在交往的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去年呢  跟某人交往过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么刨根问底的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级的时候  丹生你跟富樫君关系很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错  还想着你们是不是在交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后跟小鸟游同学之间还是三角关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我这个恋爱大师看来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说三角关系了  丹生谷同学都没跟人交往过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的女孩子还挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来经验丰富  实际上完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  要说没有也不完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是丹生你不是说你初中的时候是1200多岁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是有传言说你现在偶尔也在网上这么玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来晚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹生谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个一年级小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个反应  果然是丹生你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才  才  才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说都高中生了  怎么可能去做这么中二的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还要早起  睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在那女人旁边鬼火慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么吓人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  而且比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想知道富樫你们到哪一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么到哪一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗  就是你跟小鸟游同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此  你们是从去年学园祭开始交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们会知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一个月之后接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后总算去了约会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后在圣诞夜  你们俩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现充去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挫骨扬灰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有  你们别胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么时候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么…所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个血气方刚的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦痛致死吧  现充
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊  这时候还不说实话可是有点不地道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你把小鸟游同学给带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊里还有老师在巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才窗户上有可疑的光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像听见了女孩子的呻吟声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南无阿弥陀佛  南无阿弥陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我使用了黑暗对魔防御
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人看不见我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  为什么不接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是跟漆黑烈焰使一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩按往常的感觉来的话  肯定什么事都不会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这不是女生用的包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间里的人还醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人醒着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  那边好像有奇怪的动静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走只能趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实听到了奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  可是谁都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得在更里面一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧回房间  要是被发现了说不定会被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太跟我之间有一道屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是黑暗住民搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻碍我接近勇太的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是精神攻击的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是逃避  也没有躲着勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你很害羞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的自由活动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起逛逛吧  就我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是未满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然依旧不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我感到有什么正在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐地  渐渐地萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和六花迎来了那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小鸟游同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是今天另有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干啥呢
