Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要封印它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我们两个人的一天  开始了
